Requirement_base = "Solid theorical and practical knowledge background in the field of activity. Demonstrated strive to keep skills and knowledge up-to-date with industry development, technologies, methods, best practices, frameworks and standards in line with current direction of the Centre. General understanding of HPC environments and scientific computing, fundamental algorithms in science and engineering, and computer architecture, with practical experience. Experience installing and maintaining services in Linux and Kubernetes environments. Effective verbal and written communication skills, with full English proficiency. You are open to take on activities of a different nature, if needed."

